{"data":[{"id":563761534,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6d40f3e42e9c6434029593031e345b3","url_token":"hjihao","name":"豪豪","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f3d81cdef413892dc90b806c17a34c0d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f3d81cdef413892dc90b806c17a34c0d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6d40f3e42e9c6434029593031e345b3","user_type":"people","headline":"陌上花开 馥蕊柏然","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":91,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563761534","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8b8780ec8561af3e6d790e7df11cbd33_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273803,"updated_time":1546277366,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":31,"comment_count":17,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我看懂了他的逻辑。大框架没有错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只是他的工作是，解释了: 任意大于2的偶数总能写成两个奇数之和。(即哥德巴赫猜想的逆命题。下图是刚刚看见的，完美解释了思路)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d5e5b1fbb8080c255cd9fc302a034398_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1531\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-229e813837f2401161b32daeab057b2c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d5e5b1fbb8080c255cd9fc302a034398_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1531'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;